data.description: Approved Short Sale. Property sold AS-IS... Spacious All Brick End Unit Row House with 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths in sought after Brookland!  Main level featuring  open floor plan with hardwood floors, rear morning room and updated kitchen.  Full finished basement with kitchenette rough in, full bath and fireplace.  Rear deck overlooking nicely landscaped rear and side yard with patio.  Attached garage with additional  off street parking in rear.
